about.summary: Matrix client-server SDK for Python 2 and 3.

name: matrix_client
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "matrix_client" %}
{% set version = "0.3.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: dce3ccb8665df0d519f08e07a16e6d3f9fab3a947df4b7a7c4bb26573d68f2d5

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - pytest-runner >=5.1
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - requests

test:
  imports:
    - matrix_client

about:
  home: "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-python-sdk"
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Matrix client-server SDK for Python 2 and 3."
  doc_url: https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-python-sdk/
  dev_url: https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-python-sdk

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - setu4993
